<section id="philosophy">\
  <div class="container">\
    <div class="section-head">\
      <span class="num">05</span>\
      <span class="label">ENGINEERING PRINCIPLES</span>\
    </div>\
    <div class="sticky-pair">\
      <div class="left fade-up">\
        <div class="label">/ METHODOLOGY</div>\
        <h2>Core principles<br>guiding my practice.</h2>\
        <p>\
          The methodologies I adhere to when designing systems and writing infrastructure \
          code. These principles ensure the systems I build are maintainable, scalable, \
          and secure.\
        </p>\
      </div>\
      <div class="right">\
\
        <div class="principle fade-up">\
          <span class="num">/ 01</span>\
          <h3>Automation by Default.</h3>\
          <p>\
            Manual operations introduce human error and technical debt. If a task is \
            repeatable, it should be automated. This frees engineering teams to focus \
            on solving complex business problems rather than performing routine maintenance.\
          </p>\
        </div>\
\
        <div class="principle fade-up">\
          <span class="num">/ 02</span>\
          <h3>Infrastructure as Code (IaC).</h3>\
          <p>\
